<br>
I only bring this up because I want to know (verify my guess is correct) if it works as above, or if the dot gets dmg added only if it *starts* with Call on.<br>
<br>
Can someone shed light on this for me?  The answer is probably simple - go test it with a necro or druid, etc!  I just haven't tested it and was wondering if anyone else had yet.  If this has already been asked and answered please forgive me and link it, I didn't see a post on these specifics in the songs section here.<br>
<br>
