<br>
One thing I had noticed about Rizlona's and Call both was that if I dropped the song in the middle of a battle to mez or something, and then got it going again - even *after* the caster started casting - as long as the damage was assigned after the song icon came up, it was increased.  If the Call damage is assigned the same to dot's I'm just not sure if the damage would get increased only if the icon was up before the spell lands, or if each individual tick is taken into account.<br>
<br>
Like I said, I'll try to test this week/weekend, unless someone posts here before I do.<br>
